<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Great spell to use to practice your Divination skill. Remember that Divination is used to Gate, and since this spell only uses 5 mana each cast its a great way to build the skill up.  You can buy this spell in the Library of Ak'kron.. along with most every Misc. spell for Magicians(Summon spells, shield, and Pet).</font></td></tr></table>
