<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Gate doesn't use the divination skill.  I'm an 18th level cleric, and True North, Sense Undead, and Invis to Undead are the only three spells I have that use divination.  I believe Gate uses Alteration (hence changing reality around you).  I'm positive it's not Divination though, becauce my div skill would be a helluva lot higher than 11 by now.</font></td></tr></table>
